{"data":[{"id":560248149,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a304cb9cc5e2df7e14b9b868e082753f","url_token":"xiao-ming-tong-xue-28-93","name":"小明同学","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b3ec27a46c7315ac2b2a05da65b3fe39_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b3ec27a46c7315ac2b2a05da65b3fe39_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a304cb9cc5e2df7e14b9b868e082753f","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560248149","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545822423,"updated_time":1545822423,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e无论你的证明是否成立，兄弟，我都佩服你，在这场事件中，最珍贵的莫过于你那敢于挑战的精神\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561060237,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"aaa7cc4f31fe187a58603f663c488831","url_token":"liu-yu-zhe-44","name":"刘郁哲","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c7f9ea9f26476496a2500c31e910c928_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c7f9ea9f26476496a2500c31e910c928_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/aaa7cc4f31fe187a58603f663c488831","user_type":"people","headline":"鬼畜up主 B站ID:Alien霸霸","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561060237","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545912369,"updated_time":1545913815,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"content":"\u003cp\u003e看了好多答案都是来嘲笑你的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是来加入他们的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561504321,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a6d097ecf988531814d448865697be3d","url_token":"luo-hua-sheng-23-46","name":"罗化生","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ebb1c461788a19a1cb71e7e4c1bd7664_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ebb1c461788a19a1cb71e7e4c1bd7664_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a6d097ecf988531814d448865697be3d","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561504321","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545973437,"updated_time":1545974116,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主还是一个高中生，视野确实容易比较狭隘，说一下个人的经历以及个人证明哥德巴赫猜想的历程。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当年还在读高中的时候，也觉得考上清华北大是无上的荣光，是追求的一个重大的目标。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但几年以后，随着心态的平和，对于考上什么大学，获得什么学位之类的根本不放在心上了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e只要你有自己的研究成果，干嘛一定要有什么学位？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e即使暂时没有学术成果，自己自由自在的探索也够了，毕竟数学这个东西有一个好处就是不需要实验室，反过来说如果在某些研究院所里，各种禁锢的可能更多。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这里很多人对题主进行嘲讽，是中国教育缺乏最重要的一环：尊重教育的体现，不必在意。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e个人研究过哥德巴赫猜想，我估计你的证明很可能存在一些逻辑上的不严谨。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是不管怎么样，敢于探索，敢于思考总是好事，你可能证明哥德巴赫猜想不成功，但是你最少锤炼了你的思维，这是有助于你以后的探索其他领域的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然了，也不要过分的陷进去，毕竟你追求的是数学，而不是证明成功后的荣誉，除了哥德巴赫猜想，还有非常广阔的天地。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下是我对哥德巴赫猜想证明的一些结果\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e满足\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/search?q=%E5%93%A5%E5%BE%B7%E5%B7%B4%E8%B5%AB%E7%8C%9C%E6%83%B3\u0026amp;source=Entity\u0026amp;hybrid_search_source=Entity\u0026amp;hybrid_search_extra=%7B%22sourceType%22%3A%22answer%22%2C%22sourceId%22%3A561454475%7D\" class=\"internal\"\u003e哥德巴赫猜想\u003c/a\u003e的素数对的配对数 大致为\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=Gd_%7Bx%7D%3D%5Cprod_%7Bp_%7Bl%7D%2Fx%7Dx%281-1%2Fp_%7Bl%7D%29%281-2%2Fp%29%2B%5Csum_%7Bp%3D3%7D%5E%7B%5Csqrt%7Bx%7D%7D%5Csum_%7Bl%3D1%7D%5E%7Bq-1%7D%27%5Csum_%7Bt%3D1%7D%5E%7Bf%7D%5Cmu_%7Bq%7D%5Cmu_%7Bt%7D%7Bh%2Fq%28%28%5Cpi_%7Bt%7D%28x%2Cq%2Cl%29-%5Cpi_%7Bt%7D%28x%29%2F%5Cvarphi%28q%29%29%7D\" alt=\"Gd_{x}=\\prod_{p_{l}/x}x(1-1/p_{l})(1-2/p)+\\sum_{p=3}^{\\sqrt{x}}\\sum_{l=1}^{q-1}'\\sum_{t=1}^{f}\\mu_{q}\\mu_{t}{h/q((\\pi_{t}(x,q,l)-\\pi_{t}(x)/\\varphi(q))}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e上式中\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eq为素数p以及素数p的乘积\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ep不整除于x\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=hx%5Cequiv+l%28modq%29\" alt=\"hx\\equiv l(modq)\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Csum%E2%80%98\" alt=\"\\sum‘\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e 表示对q的缩系求和\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://www.zhihu.com/equation?tex=%5Cpi_%7Bt%7D\" alt=\"\\pi_{t}\" eeimg=\"1\"\u003e (x)表示小于x的t个素数的积\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ef为小于x 的n个素数乘积的最大的n值\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可以看到后面那一项是比较复杂的，而这一项我本来以为很简单，但是就有一个逻辑漏洞感觉处理不掉，然后苦苦思索了一年多，才发现一个看似初等的问题，实际上就是一个解析数论即等差数列中的素数定理的问题，而要解决这个问题，证明第二项是一个相对小的数，我还需要继续探索。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e说明一下曾经让我困惑的那个看起来很初等的问题是\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于一个整数X和两个素数p,q\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如何判定X=np+mq这个式子成立\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e并不是X越大，就一定成立\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e例如12=5+7\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是比12大的13就没有相应的式子成立，思索这个问题，我思索了一年，才发现必须转换为解析数论问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e总之，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1要估计问题的困难性\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2，敢于探索值得肯定\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3，不要只关注这个问题，如果对数学感兴趣，你完全可以接着自学大学数学课程，发现广阔天地，然后找到真正属于你的领域。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561870338,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"8b2ec185053fbd9ffefeb740817ca938","url_token":"li-he-hao-75","name":"雷克雅未克的雪","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/a80218e956dbe2894c5376eeae51a07f_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/a80218e956dbe2894c5376eeae51a07f_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/8b2ec185053fbd9ffefeb740817ca938","user_type":"people","headline":"学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561870338","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546009439,"updated_time":1546251993,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e题主快要公布证明了，提醒一下，在知乎公布论文可能会被数学家剽窃的。。。。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  关于这个问题， 我不能像其他答主一样嘲讽题主，因为，曾经的我也这么干过，人不中二枉少年嘛。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  初中的时候，有一段时间，疯狂的想找出素数分布的规律，也许像题主一样，沉浸在自己的所谓的激情中，确实很爽。但我能力有限，不像答主一样证明了哥猜，我最终什么都没有发现。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  后来，我听说，我们班主任，也是我们的数学老师，再跟其他班同学上课时，总会提到我，遗憾的说，我们班的那谁谁谁，要是把对数学的热情用在正确的方向，本身是可以很优秀的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  幸运的是，我没有像答主一样，把自己的前途，寄托在这些根本不可能实现的东西上，而是迷途知返，最后当然是通过考试而不是什么研究。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  我想说一句话，也是我们班主任告诉我的。一个非常业余的人研究一些非常专业的问题，除了浪费时间还有什么用呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  通过题主老师的答案，可以看出，题主是喜欢数学的，想证明哥猜想法也是很好的，Wiles不也是在10岁时就被费马大定理吸引住了，并从此选择了数学作为终身职业。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  可是，他也没有像你一样在没有系统的学习过数学前就去做这些工作啊。在他开始证明费马大定理前，已经是普林斯顿大学的教授了啊！并且在他决定向费马大定理发动冲击前，他先用18个月的时间，收集了这次战斗所必要的数学工具。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  接下来要做的，是长达10年的专心致志的努力。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  你还是高中生，不要想那么虚无缥缈的事情，如果你真的喜欢数学，那至少要考上大学后，掌握了足够的数学工具，才有可能实现你的梦想啊，虽然我觉得没戏。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  我觉得你要做的，就是把你所谓的证明撕了，烧了，扔了，总之忘了他，全身心投入高考中，想证明自己优秀，至少先拿下高考。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e  你的问题在于读书太少，想的太多……总想好高骛远，结果眼前的都看不到。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563818849,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0b3959773ae4288f6de9988fc91bfc12","url_token":"yun-qi-39-82","name":"云七","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac5fcf92dcc8c074b07ffdd05b4f773a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ac5fcf92dcc8c074b07ffdd05b4f773a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0b3959773ae4288f6de9988fc91bfc12","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563818849","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546283692,"updated_time":1546283692,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e一个刚入坑半个小时，连游戏规则都没搞懂的新手说要挑战全服最强的boss，还口出狂言说那些玩了十几年的神装大佬不知道这个boss怎么打，其实不需要什么装备就可以打败boss，只是大佬们十几年都没想到这个方法，然后说他会在三天后打这个boss给大家看。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e期间有人假装他的朋友说他不太懂游戏，理解错了一些规则，所以口出狂言希望大佬原谅，然后他说他不要无中生友，要靠自己去打过这个boss。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后他开始打boss，可是他连boss关卡入口的守卫养的猫追赶着的老鼠都打不过，直接就挂了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后一群人安慰他说不要紧，继续玩这个游戏吧，至少人家敢想敢做，不像你们连看这个boss的勇气都没。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559608484,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c08812a703566bc55861ddaa7fb73752","url_token":"theoneaboveall","name":"TheOneAboveAll","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/b4ec24aff7c30da3521ebd4b7578a7d7_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/b4ec24aff7c30da3521ebd4b7578a7d7_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c08812a703566bc55861ddaa7fb73752","user_type":"people","headline":" 普通的人生总不见得为临时起意的问题学完这一专业吧","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559608484","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545743839,"updated_time":1545885961,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e在看到错误证明前，我觉得话不能说死。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“初等数学证明不了哥德巴赫猜想”也只是个猜想，没人证明。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e万一数学家的直觉真的错了呢？历史上著名科学家犯错也不少。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e上两句话，我想了下这也只是我的猜想，可能不严谨，所以先提问求证一下。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/307132012\" class=\"internal\"\u003e为何哥德巴赫猜想不能用初等数学证明？\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e玻尔，爱因斯坦，泡利等人都作过不少错误预测。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e网上说证明出什么猜想，虽然很有可能是错的，但在找出错误前说什么都没有意义。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但是我觉得，如果真的发生了这种事，一个不被看好的高中生找到了众多数学家忽视的角度，证明了世纪难题，那人类确实有点可笑。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559541786,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7eb1fd144c72b41a5ae5b9a2077b459e","url_token":"su-ling-8","name":"苏灵","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/6ec693522_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/6ec693522_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7eb1fd144c72b41a5ae5b9a2077b459e","user_type":"people","headline":"任何学科都可与数学联姻，却不一定能生出漂亮的娃。","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559541786","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545737452,"updated_time":1546068000,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":5,"content":"\u003cp\u003e民科的所有证明都只是在玩语言游戏而枉顾其真实意义。这一点，之前那位某伟老师示范得很到位。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也许是中二期总会有些想要被别人认可，却不知道怎么办的时候吧。再有就是初中高中这一段时间里做了太多那种抓破脑壳都想不出题目，却可以用奇特的辅助线或者什么其他奇技淫巧就变得非常简单。于是觉得哥德巴赫猜想这种世界难题也是存在一个让人大附中跌眼镜的简便解法吧。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这些数学难题之所以重要不是因为它难度高，而是因为很可能现有的数学工具根本没有办法把这道题解开。换言之能解开这道题，就你发展新的数学工具，从而打开了新世界的大门。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果你只是找到了哥德巴赫猜想的反例，却没有足够价值的思路或数学工具，那就和中彩票一样，出一次大名而已。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559892098,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c93769641c19f48855286f88728ee07f","url_token":"zhang-zhi-hu-36-19","name":"张岚","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/5bcbc05cb68bd7c3e328258f344552db_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/5bcbc05cb68bd7c3e328258f344552db_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c93769641c19f48855286f88728ee07f","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559892098","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545791793,"updated_time":1545791793,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不可能的，因为哥德巴赫猜想太简单了，简单到我在知乎都能随手写出证明过程：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e由题设显然知哥德巴赫猜想成立，具体证明过程留给各位读者作为作业。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561409122,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"98d5ba60b1ca6318340a11557ab0ae1e","url_token":"luyueti1","name":"luyueti1","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4413846ba3a4001768ad62e1766016b0_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-4413846ba3a4001768ad62e1766016b0_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/98d5ba60b1ca6318340a11557ab0ae1e","user_type":"people","headline":"何以舟之，惟玉及瑶","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561409122","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545965507,"updated_time":1545966001,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e鉴于题主前几天还在纠结真命题假命题逆命题否命题的区别这种问题 怕是元旦那天会给出这样的解答：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e   由于大于2的质数都是奇数 所以两个质数加起来一定是个偶数\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eQ.E.D\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563779227,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a0f59ffe51a55247029769e9156492b4","url_token":"min-bo-tao-86","name":"闵伯韬","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-367ff4c90f993bca9563cff41bb7da9e_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-367ff4c90f993bca9563cff41bb7da9e_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a0f59ffe51a55247029769e9156492b4","user_type":"people","headline":"俺不要一直在地球村养鸡，俺想到银河市养鸡。","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563779227","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546275929,"updated_time":1546275929,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我能说我已经成功的证明了NP完全问题和霍奇猜想吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我知道很多人不相信。毕竟像我这样天才的人是几百年才能出现一个的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为了证明NP和霍奇猜想，我真的很累，现在连牛肉都吃不起了，能有哪位老哥能给我微信转账支持一下吗？我会考虑将来到普林斯顿当教授聘用你当助理的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对了，知道我是怎么证明的吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2018年12月31日夜里，长夜漫漫，无法睡眠。有个来自银河市的屌丝女外星人给我发微信，说我是地球上最帅的男人，她想成为我的女朋友。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我不知道该怎么拒绝这位外星妹妹。想了想，听说俺们地球上有七大数学难题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哎，动用我帅气的脸蛋，百度搜索了一波，随手挑了两个问题（NP和霍奇），希望能难到这位外星妹妹，毕竟虽然俺是单身，可也不想这样随便娶了一个外星妹子。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e令我万万没有想到的是，和我视频聊天的外星妹子居然随手掏出一本小学课本就把我操作了一波。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e哎，老哥们，我咋办，外星妹子明天就要开着她那架破破的二手小飞船来找我。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e有老哥能给我提个好的建议吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e要是建议好的话，明天妹子来，我让她把哥猜证明过程告诉我，到时候我私信发给你。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在线等，苦恼了一天了，难受的睡不着觉。我到底做错了什么？为啥她会看上我？难道我地球第一优秀基因被她发现了吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e难受，难受啊！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562355739,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562355739","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546077903,"updated_time":1546077903,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":7,"content":"\u003cp\u003e进清华北大的方式千千万，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么非要选择这样一条死路呢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e跳跳健美操啥的也能保送进去啊。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过说到美，我就想起了美猴王孙悟空，今年下半年中美合作的哥德巴赫猜想就要开机了，题主继续扮演孙悟空，他会努力创造一个搞笑的形象，文体两开花，弘扬高等数学文化，希望大家多多关注。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559906046,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"26edabd9810d8275718a0fa94b957ab1","url_token":"bu-zhi-dao-18-15","name":"不知道","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6af03303808557e5aabe0c59a819e12a_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-6af03303808557e5aabe0c59a819e12a_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/26edabd9810d8275718a0fa94b957ab1","user_type":"people","headline":"大学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559906046","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545792804,"updated_time":1545792804,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e最近重感冒，我尿黄，让我来。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560823648,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a80c5153e83cb9a893ac29e5a9a150d4","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560823648","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545891100,"updated_time":1545891100,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"简单明了的说，如果把上北大的难度类比赚钱买一台iPhone Xs，那么证明哥猜的难度等同于赚钱收购苹果公司。然后问出这个问题的人大概只能买个iphone6s吧。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560642537,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2c640cf6872c33ea1ef6a2832c371e9c","url_token":"he-qi-wei-53","name":"人民的气味362","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2c640cf6872c33ea1ef6a2832c371e9c","user_type":"people","headline":"准大学生","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560642537","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545876200,"updated_time":1545926123,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":45,"content":"让我们来猜一下最后的结果：\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eA.新型炒作\u003cbr\u003eB.天才出道\u003cbr\u003eC.哗众取宠\u003cbr\u003eD.年轻自大\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e看了很多回复，我坚定地支持B\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e------------------------------\u003cbr\u003e（补充）本人粗俗的见解：\u003cbr\u003eA.如果是炒作，批评那个少年有什么意思？矛头好像对错地方了吧？\u003cbr\u003eC.如果是哗众取宠，适度教育一下就行了吧？\u003cbr\u003eD.如果是年轻自大，一个批评的刺激就够大了，上千批评聚在一起，给别人带来的心理创伤会有多大？万一别人想不开了，不会有点点愧疚吗？\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e选B的用意不言而喻。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561307979,"type":"answer","an