rmal":true,"voteup_count":3,"content":"\u003cp\u003e有很多自以为“善意”的评论，让我们给一个明显哗众取宠的成年人鼓励，别去嘲讽，你们是不了解数学，还是太喜欢民科？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e民科为何会觉得自己被“官科”欺压？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e难道不就是他们身边并不了解此领域的人给予了他们足够多的“善意”和鼓励，使得他们自大了起来，而“官科”却对他们不够重视，以至于使他们产生了自己被“官科”欺压的看法吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e这位同学自认为有能力证明哥猜，这不丢人，反而是热爱数学的一种表现，毕竟谁都有相似的中二时候。但是把自己的中二丢到网络这种环境来之前，作为成年人就应当有承担这一切的觉悟。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e(换做是我，只会先把这东西交给我老师看看。就算中二我也很清楚自己的分量。)\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563781063,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"5900e4e7cd8b1c9952e0e073d2edfc78","url_token":"joker-69-85","name":"Joker","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/5900e4e7cd8b1c9952e0e073d2edfc78","user_type":"people","headline":"云大旅管","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563781063","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-b8dcd0bb232922415f5b57f34d57ed0a_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546276172,"updated_time":1546276172,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":6,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ed05242a7326b836aa17f15a8339daf_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c08183503eb51e0e95c499a865e98cbf_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ed05242a7326b836aa17f15a8339daf_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\